      "role": "user",
      "content": "small activities don't really change the fact that i'm basically invisible. i look at my Slack, my emails, the people i \"interact\" with... if i just didn't show up tomorrow, if i just stopped appearing online or even in real life, i don't think the world would even skip a beat. it feels like i'm already gone.",
